    <div class="article-teaser">
        Transport for London (TfL) today announced the extension of route 463 to Pollards Hill and Coulsdon South station from Saturday 19 December 2009.
        
    </div>



<div class="pull-quote">
        <div class="quote-body">"The extended bus route will hopefully also encourage more people to leave their cars at home"</div>
        <div class="quote-footer">
            <div class="quotee-name">William Brierly</div>
            <div class="quotee-job-title">Merton Council's cabinet member for planning and traffic management</div>
        </div>
