<p>
<p><strong>Notes to editors: </strong></p><strong></strong>
<ul>
<li>Route 463 towards Eastfields and Pollards Hill - buses will be re-routed from Manor Road along Tamworth Lane, Grove Road (stopping near Mitcham Eastfields station), Meopham Road, Rowan Road, Wide Way and terminating in South Lodge Avenue </li>
<li>Route 463 towards Wallington and Coulsdon - buses will start in South Lodge Avenue and then serve Recreation Way, Wide Way, Rowan Road, Meopham Road, Grove Road and Tamworth Lane to re-join the existing line of route at Manor Road </li>
<li>In Beddington, buses will be re-routed at Beddington Lane to serve Coomber Way, Beddington Farm Road and Marlowe Way in both directions. Route 463 will no longer serve Beddington Lane between Coomber Way and Marlowe Way. Route 455 will now serve this section<br><br></li></ul>

     

        
        
        
